Installation:

  git clone http://github.com/jameskovacs/vimfiles.git ~/vimfiles

Create NTFS hardlinks (as administrator):

  fsutil hardlink create ~/.vimrc ~/vimfiles/.vimrc

Optional NTFS hardlink if using gvim-specific settings:

  fsutil hardlink create ~/.gvimrc ~/vimfiles/.gvimrc

Based on http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/.
